sentences.english: Fools rush in where angels fear to tread .
sentences.chinese: 天使不敢踐踏的地方，蠢材蜂湧而至。

sentences.english: Crowds arrived, and I shall never forget the grand sight.
sentences.chinese: 人羣蜂湧而至，我永遠忘不了那種宏大的場面。

sentences.english: Foreigners are buying British firms in droves .
sentences.chinese: 外國人蜂湧地收購英國公司。
